// Slice 2: Parser + First Real Diagnostic
// Feature: Parse errors appear as red squiggly diagnostics in the editor.

// VALID — no errors:
StormEvents | take 10

// VALID — where with a predicate:
StormEvents | where DamageProperty > 100

// ERROR — incomplete where clause (try this to see a diagnostic):
StormEvents | where

// ERROR — missing right-hand side:
// StormEvents | where X >
